history.content:
Hello Transfer Students,

CS Advising will host drop-in advising hours specifically for you on Tuesday, September 10th from 10:00 a.m. to 12 noon in 349 Soda Hall.  Please be sure to stop by with any questions or concerns.
Note: We'll still have drop-in advising for everyone on Wednesdays.
Thank you and looking forward.
